author: Y Combinator
description:
Saurav Kumar was studying CS at UIUC just a few months ago, surrounded by cornfields and lecture halls.

Now he’s in San Francisco building Fleetline, a place where being ambitious and taking risks feels completely normal. Anyone can make that leap.

Get your application in to the winter batch by 8pm PT tomorrow. All you need is an idea: ycombinator.com/apply
title: Founder Stories: Saurav Kumar
